#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:27
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "&sweeper; helps to clean unwanted traces users leave on the system."
msgid ""
"&sweeper; helps to clean unwanted traces from &plasma; and &kde; "
"applications users leave on the system."
msgstr ""
"&sweeper; erabiltzaileek nahi gabe sisteman uzten dituzten aztarnak "
"garbitzen laguntzen du."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check all cleanup actions you would like to perform using the "
"<guibutton>Select All</guibutton> and <guibutton>Select None</guibutton> "
"buttons or by selecting/deselecting individual items from the two groups "
"<guilabel>General</guilabel> and <guilabel>Web Browsing</guilabel>"
msgstr ""
"Markatu eragin nahi dituzun garbiketa ekintza guztiak <guibutton>Guztiak "
"hautatu</guibutton> eta <guibutton>Ez hautatu ezer</guibutton> botoiak "
"erabiliz edo <guilabel>Orokorra</guilabel> eta <guilabel>Web arakaketa</"
"guilabel> bi taldeetatik elementuak banaka hautatuz"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are satisfied with your selection click the <guibutton>Clean Up</"
"guibutton> button, which immediately performs the cleanup actions you "
"selected."
msgstr ""
"Zure hautapenarekin konforme bazaude sakatu <guibutton>Garbitu</guibutton> "
"botoia, berehala eragingo ditu hautatu dituzun garbiketa ekintzak."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:52
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&sweeper; deletes the cached data used by &kde; applications from the "
#| "&kde; cache folder. To see the location of this folder enter "
#| "<userinput><command>kde4-config</command> <option>--path cache</option></"
#| "userinput> in &konsole;. Cleaning up your cached data with &sweeper; "
#| "makes it only impossible to read them &eg; using a filemanager, but it is "
#| "possible to read the raw data, which is still on the disk, using a low "
#| "level disk tool."
msgid ""
"&sweeper; deletes the cached data used by &plasma; and &kde; applications "
"from the &kde; cache folder. To see the location of this folder enter "
"<userinput><command>qtpaths</command> <option>--paths GenericCacheLocation</"
"option></userinput> in &konsole;. Cleaning up your cached data with "
"&sweeper; makes it only impossible to read them &eg; using a filemanager, "
"but it is possible to read the raw data, which is still on the disk, using a "
"low level disk tool."
msgstr ""
"&sweeper;-ek &kde;-ren aplikazioek cacheratutako datuak ezabatzen ditu &kde;-"
"ren cache karpetatik. Karpeta honen kokapena ikusteko &konsole;-n sartu "
"<userinput><command>kde4-config</command> <option>--path cache</option></"
"userinput>. &sweeper;rekin garbitutako cacheratutako datuak ezin izango dira "
"irakurri &eg; fitxategi kudeatzaile bat erabiliz, baino datu gordinak "
"irakurri daitezke, oraindik diskoan baitaude, diskoaren behe mailako tresna "
"bat erabiliz."

